{
  "name": "WF7 — New Patient Entry",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Workflow 7: New Patient Entry\n\n**Trigger:** Google Sheets Trigger (polls every minute for new rows)\n\n**Logic:**\n1. Detects when a new row is added to the Patients sheet\n2. Validates required fields (name, phone)\n3. Validates phone number format (E.164)\n4. Generates a UUID and sets default values\n5. Updates the row with the generated ID and defaults\n6. Sends a welcome WhatsApp message\n7. Logs creation event to System_Logs\n\n**Setup Notes:**\n- This workflow polls the sheet every minute (n8n trigger interval)\n- Staff should leave `id`, `status`, `message_count`, `created_at`, `updated_at` blank when adding a new patient — this workflow fills them in\n- If `id` is already set, the workflow assumes the patient was already processed and skips\n\n**Before activating:**\nSet credentials on all nodes.",
        "height": 380,
        "width": 440
      },
      "id": "77777777-7777-7777-7777-000000000001",
      "name": "Sticky Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [240, 60]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "documentId": {
          "__rl": true,
          "value": "={{ $env.GOOGLE_SHEETS_ID }}",
          "mode": "id"
        },
        "sheetName": {
          "__rl": true,
          "value": "Patients",
          "mode": "name"
        },
        "event": "rowAdded",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "77777777-7777-7777-7777-000000000002",
      "name": "New Row in Patients Sheet",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.googleSheetsTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 4,
      "position": [240, 480],
      "credentials": {
        "googleSheetsOAuth2Api": {
          "id": "REPLACE_WITH_GSHEETS_CREDENTIAL_ID",
          "name": "Google Sheets account"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "// Validate new patient row and prepare initialised record\nconst p = $input.first().json;\n\nconst errors = [];\nconst warnings = [];\n\n// Skip rows that already have an id (already processed)\nif (p.id && p.id.trim() !== '') {\n  return [{ json: { _skip: true, reason: 'Row already has an id — already processed', existing_id: p.id } }];\n}\n\n// Required field: name\nif (!p.name || p.name.trim() === '') {\n  errors.push('Missing required field: name');\n}\n\n// Required field: phone\nif (!p.phone || p.phone.trim() === '') {\n  errors.push('Missing required field: phone');\n} else {\n  const phone = p.phone.replace(/[\\s\\-().]/g, '');\n  if (!/^\\+[1-9]\\d{6,14}$/.test(phone)) {\n    errors.push(`Invalid phone format: \"${p.phone}\". Expected E.164 format like +919876543210`);\n  }\n}\n\nif (errors.length > 0) {\n  return [{\n    json: {\n      _skip: false,\n      _valid: false,\n      _errors: errors,\n      _raw: p,\n      name: p.name,\n      phone: p.phone\n    }\n  }];\n}\n\n// Generate a UUID (compatible with older JS environments)\nfunction generateUUID() {\n  return 'xxxxxxxx-xxxx-4xxx-yxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx'.replace(/[xy]/g, function(c) {\n    const r = Math.random() * 16 | 0;\n    const v = c === 'x' ? r : (r & 0x3 | 0x8);\n    return v.toString(16);\n  });\n}\n\nconst now = new Date().toISOString();\nconst normPhone = p.phone.replace(/[\\s\\-().]/g, '');\n\n// Build the initialised patient record\nconst initialised = {\n  ...p,\n  id: generateUUID(),\n  phone: normPhone,\n  status: p.status || 'pending',\n  message_count: 0,\n  response_status: 'none',\n  last_response: '',\n  health_check_sent: 'FALSE',\n  reactivation_sent: 'FALSE',\n  created_at: now,\n  updated_at: now,\n  _valid: true,\n  _skip: false,\n  _workflow: 'workflow-7-new-patient',\n  _message_type: 'welcome',\n  _to_phone: 'whatsapp:' + normPhone,\n  _message_body: `Hi ${p.name.trim()}! 👋 Welcome to ${p.clinic_name || ($env.DEFAULT_CLINIC_NAME || 'our clinic')}. We've noted your visit with ${p.doctor_name || ($env.DEFAULT_DOCTOR_NAME || 'your doctor')} and will keep you updated on your follow-up appointment.\\n\\nIf you have any questions, feel free to reply to this message.`\n};\n\nreturn [{ json: initialised }];"
      },
